rows.label: qst202804_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Gah...

rows.label: qst202804_0020
rows.name: This place is chockers with Parisax...

rows.label: qst202804_0030
rows.name: ...Parisax?

rows.label: qst202804_0040
rows.name: Not Menou's idea of fun, I can tell...

rows.label: qst202804_0050
rows.name:
What do we do?
Should we pull back?

rows.label: qst202804_0060
rows.name: No, no... I'll be fine!

rows.label: qst202804_0070
rows.name:
If that's all there is of them,
I can probably handle it, honestly...

rows.label: qst202804_0080
rows.name:
And anyway, the mineral I'm after
should be back there...

rows.label: qst202804_0090
rows.name:
I've come this far and I don't plan on
stopping now.

rows.label: qst202804_0100
rows.name: So... Here I go!

rows.label: qst202804_0110
rows.name: I'll just have to not go too close...

rows.label: qst202804_0120
rows.name:
Let's maybe move slowly to avoid
riling them up...?

rows.label: qst202804_0130
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Huh-?!

rows.label: qst202804_0140
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Ee!!! *faints*

rows.label: qst202804_0150
rows.name: Menou, are youokay?!

rows.label: qst202804_0160
rows.name:
Huh.
She's out cold.

rows.label: qst202804_0170
rows.name: We should probably not stall here...

rows.label: qst202804_0180
rows.name: Let's turn back!

rows.label: qst202804_0190
rows.name:
...Uhh?
Did I...faint?

rows.label: qst202804_0200
rows.name: ...Man. Sorry...

rows.label: qst202804_0210
rows.name: Don't even mention it.

rows.label: qst202804_0220
rows.name: Everyone's got a weakness, yeah?

rows.label: qst202804_0230
rows.name:
Yeah, but...
It's so silly...

rows.label: qst202804_0240
rows.name:
You guys came here because of my whims,
and I just went and passed out...

rows.label: qst202804_0250
rows.name: So, what we do now?

rows.label: qst202804_0260
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Hm...

rows.label: qst202804_0270
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: qst202804_0280
rows.name:
How about we wipe out the Parisax,
and call you when the coast is clear?

rows.label: qst202804_0290
rows.name:
That won't do... I know I need to
get over this and deal with things myself.

rows.label: qst202804_0300
rows.name: Tora thought Menou terrified of bugs?

rows.label: qst202804_0310
rows.name: Well... Yeah, but...

rows.label: qst202804_0320
rows.name:
Okay, here's what you do. First, we cover up
your eyes...

rows.label: qst202804_0330
rows.name: Uh, then I might hit one of you by mistake...

rows.label: qst202804_0340
rows.name:
Look Menou, you're always helping out
your allies, right?

rows.label: qst202804_0350
rows.name:
Isn't it only right to let your allies help you out
when the need arises?

rows.label: qst202804_0360
rows.name: You're not wrong there, but still...

rows.label: qst202804_0370
rows.name: Stop being so difficult...

rows.label: qst202804_0380
rows.name: I gotta admire your stubbornness though.

rows.label: qst202804_0390
rows.name: Sounds like you'll just have to go and do it then.

rows.label: qst202804_0400
rows.name: I will, won't I...

rows.label: qst202804_0410
rows.name: Talking to you all, I finally understood.

rows.label: qst202804_0420
rows.name:
I want to move forward from here and obtain
this new mineral, all on my own strength.

rows.label: qst202804_0430
rows.name:
So just because some bugs showed up, I got
all woozy? Nah, I'm not giving up that easy.

rows.label: qst202804_0440
rows.name:
If slaying some icky icky bugs is what it takes,
then I will screw up my courage and slay!

rows.label: qst202804_0450
rows.name: Uh, mind you don't blow your top there...

rows.label: qst202804_0460
rows.name: Ah, there, that's the Menou we know.

rows.label: qst202804_0470
rows.name: Yep!

rows.label: qst202804_0480
rows.name: Okay everyone, are we ready to give it another shot?

rows.label: qst202804_0490
rows.name: Always!

rows.label: qst202804_0500
rows.name:
I'll try to keep up as best as I can, I guess.
No holding back, yeah?

rows.label: qst202804_0510
rows.name:
Thank you!
Okay, let the carapace-kicking commence!
